Refer this site
https://data-flair.training/blogs/django-caching/

to check whether cache is working or not try below commands if its loading bunch of STATEs  caching is working properly if it is not loading something went wrong with configuration.

1. echo stats | nc 127.0.0.1 11211

To know updates in every two secon try the below code.
2. watch "echo stats | nc 127.0.0.1 11211"
